## Recent Updates (January 2025) ⭐

### "Include Hide as Option" Feature for Conditional Variables
- **✅ Hide Option Checkbox**: Added "Include hide as option" checkbox to conditional variable editing in both main drawer and cascading drawers
- **✅ Hidden Dimension Values**: When checked, automatically creates a "Hidden" dimension value for the conditional's paired dimension
- **✅ Canvas Invisibility**: When users select "Hidden" from dimension filter, conditional variables become completely invisible (replaced with empty string)
- **✅ Automatic Management**: System automatically creates/removes "Hidden" dimension value based on checkbox state
- **✅ Cascading Drawer Support**: Feature works identically in both main string drawer and cascading drawers for nested editing
- **✅ Consistent UX**: Seamless integration with existing dimension-based filtering system

### Conditional to String Conversion Fix
- **✅ Bidirectional Conversion**: Users can now freely convert conditional variables back to string variables using the Variable Type dropdown
- **✅ UI State Management**: Fixed dropdown reverting issue - selection now persists and updates interface correctly
- **✅ Spawn Independence**: When converting conditional → string, all spawn children remain as independent string variables
- **✅ No Data Loss**: Spawns disconnect from parent but preserve their content, names, and can still be referenced via `{{variableName}}`
- **✅ Cascading Drawer Support**: Conversion works in both main drawer and cascading drawer contexts
- **✅ Clean State Management**: Properly clears conditional-related state (spawns, hidden options) when converting to string

